sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    title Change Approval Update API - End-to-End Sequence Diagram

    participant User as Staff User<br/>(SSO)
    participant App as Integration App<br/>(GBGF Portal)
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant StaffDSP as Staff DSP<br/>(/Authenticate)
    participant WDSSO as WDSSO<br/>(SSO Provider)
    participant STS as Staff DSP<br/>(/tokenTranslate + STS)
    participant Kong as Kong API Gateway<br/>(AuthN Plugin)
    participant OpenAM as OpenAM<br/>(IdP)
    participant SNOW as ServiceNow<br/>(Change Approval)

    note over User,SNOW: ═══ PHASE 1: Staff SSO Authentication (Get AMToken) ═══

    User ->> Browser: Access Integration App
    Browser ->> App: 1. Fetch UI Resources (Non-API, unprotected)
    App -->> Browser: Return UI pages

    Browser ->> StaffDSP: 2. AJAX call /authenticate<br/>Headers: X-Client-Id, X-Client-Secret<br/>(No username/password needed)
    StaffDSP ->> StaffDSP: Verify Consumer Node
    StaffDSP ->> WDSSO: Redirect for SSO
    WDSSO -->> StaffDSP: SSO credentials validated
    StaffDSP -->> Browser: Return AMToken cookie ✅<br/>(⚠️ Use cookie only, not body token)

    note over User,SNOW: ═══ PHASE 2: Translate AMToken → Staff E2E JWT ═══

    Browser ->> App: 3. Initiate API call (with AMToken)
    App ->> STS: 4. Call /tokenTranslate<br/>with AMToken cookie
    STS ->> STS: STS translates AMToken<br/>to Staff E2E JWT
    STS -->> App: Return Staff E2E JWT ✅<br/>(⚠️ Token expires in 30 seconds!)

    note over User,SNOW: ═══ PHASE 3: Call Change Approval API (Two-Level Auth) ═══

    rect rgb(40, 60, 40)
        note right of App: Request Headers:<br/>Authorization: Basic {svc_acct}<br/>X-Staff-SNOW-E2E-Token: {jwt}<br/><br/>Request Body:<br/>{ "requestor": "{staffId}", ... }

        App ->> Kong: 5. POST hsbcc/itsm/change/approval

        note over Kong: ── Level 1: Service Account Auth ──
        Kong ->> OpenAM: 6. Validate Service Account<br/>(BasicAuth credentials)
        OpenAM -->> Kong: Service Account verified ✅<br/>E2E trust token generated

        note over Kong: ── Level 2: Staff Identity Auth ──
        Kong ->> Kong: 7. Verify X-Staff-SNOW-E2E-Token<br/>Extract StaffId from JWT
        Kong ->> Kong: 8. Match StaffId == requestor field<br/>in request payload

        alt StaffId matches requestor
            Kong ->> SNOW: 9. Forward approved request<br/>(with e2e-token-trust-header)
            SNOW ->> SNOW: Process CR Approve/Reject
            SNOW -->> Kong: CR Result (Approved/Rejected)
            Kong -->> App: 200 OK - CR Updated ✅
            App -->> Browser: Display result to user
        else StaffId does NOT match requestor
            Kong -->> App: 403 Forbidden ❌<br/>(Impersonation blocked)
        end
    end

    note over User,SNOW: ═══ ERROR HANDLING ═══

    rect rgb(60, 40, 40)
        note over App,Kong: If AMToken expired (401 from AuthN)
        App ->> StaffDSP: Re-call /authenticate (SSO)
        StaffDSP -->> App: New AMToken cookie
        App ->> STS: Re-call /tokenTranslate
        STS -->> App: New Staff E2E JWT
        App ->> Kong: Retry API call with new tokens
    end
